code: @Override public Producer createProducer() throws Exception {     return new JCacheProducer(this, cacheConfiguration). }
@Override public Consumer createConsumer(Processor processor) throws Exception {     return new JCacheConsumer(this, processor). }
@Override protected void doStart() throws Exception {     cacheManager = JCacheHelper.createManager(cacheConfiguration). }
@Override protected void doStop() throws Exception {     if (cacheManager != null) {         cacheManager.close().     } }
